txt.en: 'To the minds of my kin at Azanulbizar, there was little, if any, difference between goblins and Orcs. All who swore allegiance to Azog would meet the same fate!'
Many were the goblins slain during the Battle of Azanulbizar.
'What is a goblin but a small-boned Orc? Many more soon fell to my hammer!'
